Program to generate a constant bitrate of data. Ideal for testing data
being pushed over a network/wifi connection.

Syntax: ./constant_bitrate fromfilename tofilename bitrate packetsize
   filenames may be - to indicate stdin or stdout

Example:

On machine #1:

./constant_bitrate /dev/zero - 10000000 1024 | netcat 192.168.1.10 7772

On machine #2:

netcat 7772
